title: Female Outlook on BASE (FOBASE)
description:
When you enter BASE, you open up an amazing new world. You travel, meet new people and begin to believe that things you couldn&#039;t ever imagine are now real... and all this time you learn. You keep your eyes open and try to notice, understand and remember the sightest details of what&#039;s happening around you. You take small, careful steps, balancing between fear and extasy. 

I want to show you what i see standing next to my friends at the exit poing or flying with them in the air. "Female Outlook on BASE" is a year of my life. This is a movie about my friends, about places we have been to together, about what we&#039;ve learned during that time. 
See this world with my eyes, feel what i feel playing this game. 

Lika NIGHT139
